Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你…弄壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你！
